{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_09_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 目に見える結果がないと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（愛には体調が戻るまで、仕事も学校も休んでもらう）\n（ことにしたが……寮に一人きりにするのは、心配だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’ve decided to let Ai take time off work and school until she recovers‚）\n（but… I’m worried about leaving her alone in the dorm.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（連絡を入れて、少し様子を見に行ってみるか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I should check in on her and see how she’s doing…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8112701733,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9587.1195953,
          "startTime": 19.3983897686
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4016102314
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4016102314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（結局寮につくまで、メッセの返信はなかったが……）\n（……ん？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She didn’t reply to my messages until I got to the dorm…）\n（…Hm?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.7698640664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがいる……！？\n夢じゃない、よね……えっと、お、お疲れ様です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san is here…?!\nIt’s not a dream‚ is it…? U-um‚ g-good work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.2421316624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日は大変ご迷惑をおかけしました……\nそのうえ病院にまで連れて行ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so sorry for all the trouble I caused yesterday…\nOn top of that‚ you took me to the hospital…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、お礼が先？　それともお詫び？\nまず何から言えば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ should I thank you first? Or apologize?\nWhat should I say first…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9361895469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2030374686
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "まずは落ち着いてくれ。それと気にしないでくれ\nそれより具合はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ calm down. And don’t worry about it.\nMore importantly‚ how are you feeling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1246095181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4653976917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ただの風邪と過労でしたし、昨日より元気です！\n今、ちょうど水を飲みに行こうと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it was just a cold and some overwork. I feel better than yesterday!\nI was just about to go get some water…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、良かった。少しだけ安心したよ\nところで愛、昼食は食べたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s good. I’m a little relieved.\nBy the way‚ Ai‚ have you had lunch?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.7091143448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……まだです。食欲がなくて……\n何か食べて薬を飲まないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Not yet. I don’t have much of an appetite…\nI need to eat something and take my medicine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ昼食は俺が用意するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I’ll prepare lunch for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5778228918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3613149403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "用意？　もしかして作るんですか……？\n{user}さんの手料理……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Prepare? You mean… you’re going to make it…?\n{user}-san’s cooking…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "簡単なものしか作れないから、期待はしないでくれ\n……今日は寮に誰もいないから、心細いんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can only make simple things‚ so don’t get your hopes up.\n…You must be lonely being alone in the dorm today‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.1823352574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、全部私のせいですから\n私が急にダウンしちゃったせいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s all my fault.\nBecause I suddenly collapsed‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.9000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "私がやるはずだった仕事の代打に行ってもらってるので\nみんなに申し訳ないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "everyone’s covering for what I had to do.\nI’m so sorry to everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.8873465934
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "困った時は、お互いに助け合えばいいんだ\nそれじゃあ、少し待っててくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We should help each other out when we’re in trouble.\nSo just wait here for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.3521995304
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます\n楽しみに待ってますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.\nI’ll be looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.4666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 115.033038465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの作ってくれた親子うどん\nとっても美味しかったです、ごちそうさまでした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oyako udon {user}-san made\nwas so delicious. Thank you for the meal!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "卵もうどんもとろっとろで……最高です！\n元気になったら自分でも作ってみようと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The egg and the udon were so soft… It’s the best!\nI think I’ll try making it myself once I’m better!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.9333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "愛には、ラーメンの方が良かったんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wouldn’t you have preferred ramen‚ Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6849432388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "もう、冗談ばっかり！　私だって\n一年中ラーメンばっかり食べてる訳じゃありませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you’re always joking! I don’t\neat ramen all year round‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はは、ごめん。残さず食べてくれて、安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ sorry. I’m glad you ate it all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1924033879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "お腹も一杯になって……少し、落ち着きました\n{user}さん、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My stomach is full… and I feel a little calmer now.\nThank you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "私が話せるようになるまで、待っててくれたんですよね\n昨日話せなかったこと……今、聞いてもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You waited for me until I was ready to talk‚ didn’t you?\nCan you… listen to what I couldn’t say yesterday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4206486399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ、聞かせてくれ。自分のペースでいいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ tell me. Take your time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9445801814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "はい……東京シーサイドとのタイアップの後\n私達がライブバトルをしたの、覚えてますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay… After the tie-up with Tokyo Seaside‚\ndo you remember the live battle we had?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.9000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルには勝ちましたけど……\nでも、ギリギリでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won the live battle…\nbut… it was a close call.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.2666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "その時、思っちゃったんです\n私達はこんなに頑張って、実力だってついて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that time‚ I thought…\nWe worked so hard‚ we got better‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "魅せるパフォーマンスだって\n出来てるつもりだったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and we thought we were able to\nput on captivating performances…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.7666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、自分で思ってるより\n実力も頑張りも、足りてなかったのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But maybe… we’re not as skilled\nor as hard-working as we think we are…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.4666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか……愛は努力を重ね、少しずつだが自信も）\n（ついてきていた。そんな中での、あの結果だったから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see… Ai worked hard‚ and her confidence was growing little by little.）\n（That’s why that result was such a blow to her.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.2000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "……それに……それにあの時から、莉央さんと葵さんも\n少しおかしくて……ぎくしゃくしてるっていうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…And… and since then‚ Rio-san and Aoi-san have been\nacting a little strange… They’re… awkward‚ I guess?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.3026643597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "だから先輩達には相談し辛いし\n私もこころもどうしていいか分からなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it’s hard to talk to our seniors‚\nand Kokoro and I don’t know what to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.3000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "……だから、悩みごとがあれば\n筋肉に聞けばいいと思ったんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ I thought if I had any worries‚\nI should just ask my muscles…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.8666727702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、それはどういうことだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ what do you mean by that…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.7019626536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "筋トレすれば、頭がすっきりした感じがしますから\n答えが出るまで、毎日筋トレメニューを増やし続けて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I do muscle training‚ my head feels clearer.\nSo I kept adding more and more to my workout routine until I found an answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.3333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai024.m4a",
      "text": "一昨日はいよいよ腹筋が三千回の大台で……\nなんとかやりきったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The day before yesterday‚ I finally reached the milestone of 3‚000 sit-ups…\nI somehow managed to do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.0578211545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "思うところはあるが、愛らしいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a lot to say about that‚ but… that's so like you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.5633588711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai025.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もやもやは全然晴れなくて\n気になってちゃんと眠ることも出来なくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the fog in my head didn’t clear at all‚\nand I couldn’t sleep properly because I was so worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.2333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai026.m4a",
      "text": "それで最低のコンディションのまま現場に……\n本当にすみませんでした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I ended up going to work in the worst condition…\nI’m really sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.9000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai027.m4a",
      "text": "原因は、私が自己管理を出来ていなかったせいです\n以前も{user}さんに注意されたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason is that I wasn’t managing myself properly.\nAlthough you warned me about this before‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.1333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai028.m4a",
      "text": "そんな申し訳なさに、疲れと寝不足が重なったのか\nこの間は、全然涙が止まらなくなっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess it was a mix of guilt‚ exhaustion‚ and lack of sleep.\nAnd even I couldn’t stop myself from crying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.8000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。誰にも相談出来なくて辛かったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. It must have been tough not being able to talk to anyone about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.1579969168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai029.m4a",
      "text": "これは、私だけの問題じゃない……\nLizNoirの、これからのことだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn’t just my problem…\nIt’s about LizNoir’s future…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.7666727702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai030.m4a",
      "text": "相談してどうにかなることじゃないって……\n自分達で解決しなきゃいけないって、分かってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know it’s not something that can be solved by talking about it…\nWe have to solve it ourselves‚ I understand that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.1333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai031.m4a",
      "text": "でも、{user}さんに話すことが出来て\nすっきりしました。ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I feel better after talking to you‚ {user}-san.\nI feel relieved. Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 322.5333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "……それで、悩みは解決出来そうなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ do you think you can solve your problem now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 326.4772874755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai032.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……まだ解決出来そうにありません\nやっぱり筋トレと頑張りが足りないんでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… I don’t think it can be solved yet.\nMaybe I need to do more muscle training and work harder…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.3666727702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "筋トレはやり過ぎだ。それに俺は\nリズノワの、愛の頑張りが足りないとは全く思わない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re doing too much muscle training. And I don’t\nthink LizNoir‚ or Ai's efforts‚ are lacking at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 343.3333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai033.m4a",
      "text": "でも、結果に繋がってないじゃないですか……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… it’s not leading to results…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 347.5823435231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai034.m4a",
      "text": "あ……すみません、大きな声を出しちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I’m sorry‚ I raised my voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 351.1043844306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai035.m4a",
      "text": "けど……目に見える結果がないと、不安なんです\n私には、頑張る以外、何が出来るのか分からないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I get anxious when there are no visible results.\nI don’t know what else I can do besides work hard‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 361.8333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai036.m4a",
      "text": "……それが、怖いんです\nだからもっともっと頑張るしかないのかな、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…and… that scares me.\nSo I have to work even harder‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 371.7666727702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないよ\n俺から見れば、愛達は十分に結果を出している",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not true.\nFrom my perspective‚ you guys are already getting plenty of results.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 377.9333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "頑張ることに行き詰まったなら\n別のやり方を考えてみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re stuck in a rut‚\nlet’s think of a different approach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 383.892619463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai037.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　それってどういうことですか？",
